\f0\fs26 \cf0 A ship or boat has many of the same hazards found in shoreside workplaces, but in addition it has the danger of drowning. Fortunately, ships are equipped with several specialized pieces of safety equipment designed to help protect you in the watery environment. These include: life preservers, work vests, immersion suits, and thermal protective aids.\
\
